#

Spicy Breakfast Bean and Corn Toast

$8.5
450 kcal

Allergens:

GlutenEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Protein

Tags:

BreakfastSpicyComfort Food

Description

A vibrant and spicy twist on breakfast with a hearty bean and corn topping on crispy toast, finished with a drizzle of Cholula hot sauce.

Ingredients

  • Eggs: 2
  • Whole Grain Bread: 2 slices
  • Canned Black Beans: 1 cup
  • Corn (fresh or canned): 1 cup
  • Cholula Hot Sauce: to taste
  • Olive Oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
